headline: 2023 Workout Stations and Movements
text:
This is reference post containing the 2023 Workout Stations and Movements.

This was the OG Event, and I didnt participate. In ways was a big trial event for what it has become today.

The 2023 details are NOT current available on the REDLINE Fitness Games at time of writing. So I am providing her for reference purposes.

If you have any questions, requests or need any explanations, please stick it in the feedback form. and I'll do my best to address.

Thanks,

Steve
